{"tid":1911111,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"SQQQ同TQQQ 隔夜／長線投資一問！","createTime":"2020-03-05T06:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T13:24:09.000Z","uid":323911,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8f3136b32105ef45fe4ddf46e26f39f69df63a4a","tid":1911111,"uid":323911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:32:59.000Z","msg":"成日聽d ching講話SQQQ、TQQQ 唔可以隔夜持有或長線投資，我睇埋錢家有道都係咁講：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槓桿及反向產品的投資目標是提供相等於相關指數表現特定倍數或特定相反倍數的單日回報，並非為持有超過一天的投資而設。假如持有槓桿及反向產品超過一天，有關產品的累計回報未必相等於相關指數特定倍數或特定相反倍數的累計回報。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ifec.org.hk/web/tc/investment/investment-products/leveraged-and-inverse-products/long-term-holding-risk.page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifec.org.hk%2Fweb%2Ftc%2Finvestment%2Finvestment-products%2Fleveraged-and-inverse-products%2Flong-term-holding-risk.page&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=0f8e094f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ifec.org.hk/web/tc/investment/investment-products/leveraged-and-inverse-products/long-term-holding-risk.page</a><br />\n<br />\n但我簡單d咁諗，只要SQQQ／TQQQ嘅賣出價＞買入價 唔係就賺喇咩？唔洗理長／短線持有？<br />\n<br />\n求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79528c32a175f2028faa4a033e2a1bf3d1e39ca0","tid":1911111,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:41:43.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n你睇中牛熊市無問題"},{"pid":"096768f5e660ed5d0f08a8c7913431789c714d8a","tid":1911111,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"留名睇教學"},{"pid":"83ed3b7c3651eb24e1844e003ce3691c71ba6585","tid":1911111,"uid":19962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:53:24.000Z","msg":"會有損耗"},{"pid":"1d08872630728b345f84464434fb54beddc91dd2