hk/web/tc/investment/investment-products/leveraged-and-inverse-products/long-term-holding-risk.page</a><br />\n<br />\n但我簡單d咁諗，只要SQQQ／TQQQ嘅賣出價＞買入價 唔係就賺喇咩？唔洗理長／短線持有？<br />\n<br />\n求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:12:46.000Z","msg":"你可以咁講<br />\n<br />\n長線持有的實際問題係，加上你hold兩日，第一日升1％，第二日跌1％，總和唔計管理費係1.01*0.99=0.9999"},{"pid":"97f63e719b65228ee8357936820eda9673628433","tid":1911111,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:33:48.000Z","msg":"雖然一般而言 係唔應該揸槓桿ETF<br />\n<br />\n但從結果論 過去十年長揸TQQ係贏QQQ好多 <br />\n因為QQQ過去十年係單邊大牛市 上落波幅唔大"},{"pid":"7c0a859f0b2d4e5ac4b11e2d6a91e7220776157b","tid":1911111,"uid":298759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:41:41.000Z","msg":"主因係佢百分比每日結算<br />\n你睇錯方向一日<br />\n你要返岩既方向仲要再高d先回得返<br />\n<br />\n你睇岩方向又日日都岩方向係冇問題<br />\n不過邊度黎咁多十二月/一月爆升市或者上個禮拜爆跌市"},{"pid":"8efedf31a1d0eab92eaef0644a373da578e6607a","tid":1911111,"uid":217415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f3136b32105ef45fe4ddf46e26f39f69df63a4a","tid":1911111,"uid":323911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:32:59.000Z","msg":"成日聽d ching講話SQQQ、TQQQ 唔可以隔夜持有或長線投資，我睇埋錢家有道都係咁講：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槓桿及反向產品的投資目標是提供相等於相關指數表現特定倍數或特定相反倍數的單日回報，並非為持有超過一天的投資而設。假如持有槓桿及反向產品超過一天，有關產品的累計回報未必相等於相關指數特定倍數或特定相反倍數的累計回報。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ifec.org.hk/web/tc/investment/investment-products/leveraged-and-inverse-products/long-term-holding-risk.page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifec.org.hk%2Fweb%2Ftc%2Finvestment%2Finvestment-products%2Fleveraged-and-inverse-products%2Flong-term-holding-risk.page&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=0f8e094f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.if